overview: The user initiated a request to significantly improve the aesthetics
  of their sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was too generic. The
  approach involved a comprehensive overhaul of the visual design. Key decisions
  included adopting a calming, sleep-themed color palette with deep indigos,
  purples, and teal accents, replacing the previous corporate blue/gray scheme.
  The main form layout was enhanced with decorative background elements and a
  redesigned progress indicator. The intro section was transformed with a hero
  element and feature cards, and all core UI components like checkboxes, radio
  buttons, sliders, and progress bars received a polished, modern update. The
  report section was also restyled for a more professional look. The outcome is
  an application with a more personalized, trustworthy, and visually appealing
  interface, moving away from a template-driven appearance to one that resonates
  with a sleep health context.
